{{for|the currency|Gold}} {{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = G |image = consul g.png |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = Male |haircolor = |eyecolor = |affiliation = [[Consul]]s |voiceactorjp = |voiceactoreng = |appearances = {{XC3}} }} '''G''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == G is the [[Consul]] of [[Colony Gamma]]. Sometime prior to Oleg coming to Colony Gamma, G made an oath with him: ''"To impart wisdom to those who will succeed us. To teach them of strength, and the tenets of battle. That this humble wish should spark, we pledge to never divulge the secrets of the past."'' He then gave him the name of [[Teach]], and made him an educator. {{clr}}
