{{Infobox quest |name = Gauntlet: Pro |image = XC3 Challenge Battle Mode.png |description = "At pro level, road to victory eeeeven looonger! Strengthen Emblems at Prize X-change for key to success!" |giver = [[Nopon Archsage]] |location = [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]] |prereqs = Main Story completed |difficultyCB3 = 5 |rewards = }} '''Gauntlet: Pro''' is an [[Archsage's Gauntlet]] [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge]] in {{XC3}}. It can be challenged by talking to the [[Nopon Archsage]] in the [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]], available as downloadable content from Vol. 3 of the Expansion Pass. Clearing this challenge with at least B rank for the first time will unlock the Throwback A [[Clothing|outfit]] for [[Mio]] and clearing with at least A rank for the first will unlock the Throwback A outfit for [[Noah]].
